  <lyrics>[V1]
 Kollan suma Dios Awqui  
 Qhuyaptayasitaya.
 Yatichitay nayaru
 Arunacam parlaña.
 
[C]
 Khespiyir Dios Awqui
 Ch'amamay churita.
 Kollan arunacam
 Parlañajjataqui.
 
[V2]
 Irpaquitay Dios Awqui
 Kollan Ajayumampi,
 Asqui munasiñamat
 Khananchañajjataqui.
 
[V3]
 Yuspagarsmaw Dios Awqui
 Nayar munatamata.
 Wiñayaw yupaycháma
 Machak k'ochunacampi.
 
 </lyrics></song>